name: AE Smith
homepage_content: About AE Smith | AE Smith We believe there is a better way… A better way, created by a passionate team dedicated to delivering the best solution every time. As a values-based business, we focus on people’s health and well-being, trusted relationships with customers and partners and delivering on our promises. About AE Smith More than just a mechanical services contractor with a 120-year history, AE Smith is a recognised market leader in heating, ventilation, air conditioning and refrigeration (HVAC&R), building services, plumbing, electrical and painting. With the development of the AES Insights business, AE Smith also provides advisory and building optimisation services that help our customers meet the challenges they face creating a more modern, environmentally sustainable and energy efficient asset. Recently back in private hands, alongside sister company, the Envar Group, AE Smith is focused on delivering the agile and innovative solutions that our customers desire. With a Board and Executive Management team with decades of experience in ASX listed companies, we also know that strong governance, robust systems and processes that mitigate risk for our people and customers support these objectives. We provide a fully integrated offering to look after every lifecycle stage of your building’s assets—from design to optimised maintenance—ensuring its longevity and implementing sustainable energy-efficient practices. Our integrated approach focuses on significantly streamlining operations, reducing risk, and applying innovative and energy and cost-saving solutions. We have 8 offices located in Brisbane, Cairns, Gold Coast, Mackay, Melbourne, Rockhampton, Sydney and Townsville. We provide clients with a single point of contact and offer tailored, flexible solutions engineered to meet your specific current and future needs. Contact us Brisbane, QLD 60-62 Qantas Drive, Brisbane Airport QLD 4007 E: Service.SEQ@aesmith.com.au T: 1300 313 313 Cairns, QLD 89-91 Cook Street, Cairns QLD 4870 E: nqdispatch@aesmith.com.au T: +61 7 4729 8555 Gold Coast, QLD 2/24 Export Drive, Molendinar QLD 4214 E: Service.SEQ@aesmith.com.au T: 1300 313 313 Mackay, QLD 16 Ginger Street, Paget QLD 4740 E: CQService@aesmith.com.au T: 1300 313 313 Melbourne 26 Cato Street Hawthorn East, VIC 3123 E: Service.Vic@aesmith.com.au T: 1300 313 313 Rockhampton, QLD 1-28 Chappell Street, Kawana QLD 4701 E: CQService@aesmith.com.au T: 1300 313 313 Sydney, NSW 12 Waltham Street Artarmon, NSW 2064 E: Service.NSW@aesmith.com.au T: 1300 313 313 Townsville, QLD 301 Woolcock Street, Garbutt QLD 4814 E: nqdispatch@aesmith.com.au T: +61 7 4729 8555 The AE Smith group – back in caring, private hands since 2023.
